      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] occasionally we had some fights with the non-Jewish kids, which maybe was normal.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)",
        "Feelings and thoughts"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we used to get along.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe not very well, but we [LAUGHS] used to get along.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Same way.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Same way.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, that-- there was no, not, there was no problem where there was a segregated customers or something like that.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then, naturally, in the school, we used to have some fights occasionally, now and then.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Daily life (childhood)"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely.",
      "recall": false,
