      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very cramped, very cramped.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can imagine that-- I don't know how many thousands of Jews used to live in a big sections, and all of a sudden the whole ghetto was maybe [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] five or six blocks versus a, a half a city, because Cracow had a big Jewish population.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big Jewish population.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how many thousands of Jews were there, but there was-- I don't know if it was 50,000 or 70,000.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was very cramped.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't remember how many thousand people.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was very cramped conditions.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Captivity"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Fortunately, for me and my father that I'm-- on one occasion, where we had to-- it was before we went to ghetto-- we had to register to-- every Jewish person had to register, to go to [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] labor, labor office, like.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans used to come, come to the labor office, and they used to request so many Jewish workers for their purpose, whatever purpose it was, to clean the facility, to wash or to carry coal or to carry furniture or whatever it was.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Forced labor"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one time I was picked up by [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the German Gestapo headquarters, whoever it was.",
